sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as User / Browser
    participant API    as Backend (Spring Boot)
    participant DB     as MySQL DB
    participant Filter as JWT Filter

    Note over Client, API: Authentication Phase
    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/login {username, password}
    API->>DB: SELECT user WHERE username = ?
    DB-->>API: User row (passwordHash, roles, allowedEnvs)
    API->>API: BCrypt.verify(password, hash)

    alt Valid credentials
        API->>API: Sign JWT (HMAC-SHA256, TTL 24h)
        API-->>Client: 200 OK — { token, expiresIn: 86400 }
    else Invalid
        API-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over Client, Filter: Authorization Phase (all subsequent requests)
    Client->>Filter: GET /api/v1/... Authorization: Bearer <token>
    Filter->>Filter: Parse & verify signature / expiry
    alt Token valid
        Filter->>Filter: Extract claims to SecurityContext
        Filter->>API: Forward with authenticated principal
        API-->>Client: 200 OK — requested resource
    else Token invalid / expired
        Filter-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end
